4208.html \n  |title=Bereza, polski ob\u00f3z koncentracyjny\n  |date=19 April 2008\n  |trans-title=Bereza, a Polish concentration camp\n  |publisher=[[Gazeta Wyborcza|wyborcza.pl]]\n  |accessdate=29 October 2015\n  |ref= {{Harvid|Garlicki|2008}}}}\n:{{Cite book\n  |last= Gawryszewski  |first= Andrzej  |year= 2005\n  |title= Ludno\u015b\u0107 Polski w XX wieku  |trans-title= The Population of Poland in the 20th Century\n  |location= Warsaw  |publisher= [[Polish Academy of Sciences|Polska Akademia Nauk]]\n  |isbn= 83-87954-66-7  |ref= harv}}\n:{{Cite book\n  |last= Gella  |first= Aleksander  |year= 1989\n  |title= Development of Class Structure in Eastern Europe: Poland and Her Southern Neighbours\n  |location= Albany, NY  |publisher= [[SUNY Press]]\n  |isbn= 978-0-887-06833-1  |ref= harv}}\n:{{Cite book\n  |last= Gierowski |first= J\u00f3zef  |authorlink= J\u00f3zef Andrzej Gierowski |year= 1986a\n  |title= Historia Polski 1505\u20131764  |trans-title= History of Poland 1505\u20131764\n  |location= Warsaw  |publisher= [[Polish Scientific Publishers PWN|PWN]]\n  |isbn= 83-01-03732-6  |ref= harv}}\n:{{Cite book\n  |last= Gierowski |first= J\u00f3zef  |authorlink= J\u00f3zef Andrzej Gierowski |year= 1986b\n  |title= Historia Polski 1764\u20131864  |trans-title= History of Poland 1764\u20131864\n  |location= Warsaw  |publisher= [[Polish Scientific Publishers PWN|PWN]]\n  |isbn= 83-01-03732-6  |ref= {{Harvid|Gierowski|1986b}}}}\n:{{Cite web\n  |last= Henig  |first= Ruth  |date= 10 March 2011\n  |title= Versailles and Peacemaking\n  |url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/worldwars/wwone/versailles_01.shtml  |accessdate= 30 August 2018\n  |publisher= [[BBC|www.bbc.co.uk]]  |ref= harv}}\n:{{cite encyclopedia |last= Herbst |first= Stanis\u0142aw \n|title= Tadeusz Ko\u015bciuszko |work= Polski S\u0142ownik Biograficzny, 439 pages |volume= 14 |year= 1969 \n|location= Warszawa|publisher= Instytut Historii (Polska Akademia Nauk)|language= Polish\n|ref= harv}}\n:{{cite news\n  |last=